{
  "id": "MAT.28",
  "bibleId": "de4e12af7f28f599-01",
  "number": "28",
  "bookId": "MAT",
  "reference": "Matthew 28",
  "copyright": "PUBLIC DOMAIN except in the United Kingdom, where a Crown Copyright applies to printing the KJV. See http://www.cambridge.org/about-us/who-we-are/queens-printers-patent",
  "verseCount": 20,
  "content": [
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "1",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:1"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "1",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "In the end of the sabbath, as it began to dawn toward the first ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "day",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.28.1",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.28.1"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " of the week, came Mary Magdalene and the other Mary to see the sepulchre. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "2",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:2"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "2",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And, behold, there was a great earthquake: for the angel of the Lord descended from heaven, and came and rolled back the stone from the door, and sat upon it. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.2",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.2"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "3",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:3"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "3",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "His countenance was like lightning, and his raiment white as snow: ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.3",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "4",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:4"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "4",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And for fear of him the keepers did shake, and became as dead ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.4",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "men",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.28.4",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.28.4"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": ". ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.4",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "5",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:5"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "5",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And the angel answered and said unto the women, Fear not ye: for I know that ye seek Jesus, which was crucified. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.5",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.5"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "6",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:6"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "6",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "He is not here: for he is risen, as he said. Come, see the place where the Lord lay. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "7",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:7"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "7",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And go quickly, and tell his disciples that he is risen from the dead; and, behold, he goeth before you into Galilee; there shall ye see him: lo, I have told you. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "8",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:8"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "8",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And they departed quickly from the sepulchre with fear and great joy; and did run to bring his disciples word.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.8",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.8"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "9",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:9"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "9",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "¶ And as they went to tell his disciples, behold, Jesus met them, saying, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.9",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "All hail.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.28.9",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.28.9"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " And they came and held him by the feet, and worshipped him. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.9",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "10",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:10"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "10",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Then said Jesus unto them, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "Be not afraid: go tell my brethren that they go into Galilee, and there shall they see me.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.28.10",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.28.10"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "11",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:11"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "11",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "¶ Now when they were going, behold, some of the watch came into the city, and shewed unto the chief priests all the things that were done. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.11",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.11"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "12",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:12"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "12",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And when they were assembled with the elders, and had taken counsel, they gave large money unto the soldiers, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.12",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.12"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "13",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:13"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "13",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Saying, Say ye, His disciples came by night, and stole him ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.13",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.13"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "away",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.28.13",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.28.13"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " while we slept. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.13",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.13"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "14",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:14"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "14",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And if this come to the governor’s ears, we will persuade him, and secure you. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.14",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.14"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "15",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:15"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "15",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "So they took the money, and did as they were taught: and this saying is commonly reported among the Jews until this day.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.15",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.15"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "16",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:16"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "16",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "¶ Then the eleven disciples went away into Galilee, into a mountain where Jesus had appointed them. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.16",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.16"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "17",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:17"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "17",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And when they saw him, they worshipped him: but some doubted. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.17",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.17"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "18",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:18"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "18",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And Jesus came and spake unto them, saying, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.18",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.18"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "All power is given unto me in heaven and in earth.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.28.18",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.28.18"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "para",
      "type": "tag",
      "attrs": {
        "style": "p"
      },
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "19",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:19"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "19",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "¶ Go ye therefore, and teach all nations, baptizing them in the name of the Father, and of the Son, and of the Holy Ghost:",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.28.19",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.28.19"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.19",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.19"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "20",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "MAT 28:20"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "20",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "wj"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "Teaching them to observe all things whatsoever I have commanded you: and, lo, I am with you alway, ",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.28.20",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.28.20"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "name": "char",
              "type": "tag",
              "attrs": {
                "style": "add"
              },
              "items": [
                {
                  "text": "even",
                  "type": "text",
                  "attrs": {
                    "verseId": "MAT.28.20",
                    "verseOrgIds": [
                      "MAT.28.20"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "text": " unto the end of the world.",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "MAT.28.20",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "MAT.28.20"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " Amen.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "MAT.28.20",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "MAT.28.20"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
